require(haemdata)
use_pinboard("onedrive")

metadata_mmu <- get_pin("metadata_mmu.csv")

Mice

Haemdata includes 949 samples from 124 mice (across 1891 sequencing runs). Metadata are parsed by functions in import_metadata.R and collated by the make_metadata_mmu() function, sourced in the same document.

Missingness

Metadata have been parsed from many sources in various formats and undoubtedly require close inspection and correction. Please report any issues.

Human datasets

Haemdata includes SummarisedExperiments from human patients with MDS (EGAD00001003891), AML patients at diagnosis, remission and relapse from Kim et al 2020,
and FLT3 AML patients from the COH Biobank. Metadata are parsed from public databases but its not great and will require manual inspection before its of any use.
